name: Laptop-keys.com
overview:
Laptop-keys.com offers replacement laptop keys at a fraction of the cost for a new keyboard. Repair your keyboard for less than $5. With free video illustrated installation instructions, anybody can repair their laptop keyboard in just minutes. No technical skills required. These are genuine, OEM keyboard keys that will fit perfect the first time, every time. Same day shipping on all orders before 5pm PST.

We started out in Fall of 2006 with one goal: Provide single replacement laptop keys for the fraction of the cost of replacing the whole keyboard. Since then, we have grown and become the industry leader in the laptop keyboard repair industry. We cover about 95% of all laptop models and continue to grow every day. Currently, we support around 9000 models and have over 4 million keys on hand ready to ship. We ensure fast and reliable service to all our customers and offer shipping services from economy First Class all the way to Next Day Express Air. We also ship worldwide to any country. Technicians are on hand every day to answer any questions you may have about our products or services.
